{"tid":1911080,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"小心狗鐵查飛狗","createTime":"2020-03-05T06:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T08:06:55.000Z","uid":308377,"like":51,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f3f5b784d76219dbee1cf9eab5b9ecfc9bd0c8e5","tid":1911080,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"近排小咗裝修黨鐵站<br />\n班黃衫好撚惡死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日企出泥捉手足跳閘同綠卡<br />\n仲要好大口氣<br />\n態度又閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見撚到就眼火爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以各位逼住用鐵嘅連登仔要小心以下事項<br />\n<br />\n使用者：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旁觀者：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e124d371c24f12b1311a3e492d37cb95555e93","tid":1911080,"uid":80164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee8cb9601acf741c59dcefef5a41f7e24f88a10","tid":1911080,"uid":101290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"小心啲啦，睇清楚先入，有就換個入口啦"},{"pid":"12aeae0e6baf97fe5c3b6febd4be9b8b037b428b","tid":1911080,"uid":172040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"cacbda8e9928764676dd37cef17a0d92a3d427c2","tid":1911080,"uid":308377,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"借圖活用：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ak3L7tF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fak3L7tF.png&h=a7bc184a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中紅標記為狗鐵附例紙，未能出示有效車票會罰款$500<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvz3T8G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frvz3T8G.png&h=4088a3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅標記所指為查飛機，會check到八達通最近十次交易記錄，同埋通常禁企，都一定係查飛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbecb4b4926d4f4365ec0283fead49e37186c158","tid":1911080,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0e124d371c24f12b1311a3e492d37cb95555e93","tid":1911080,"uid":80164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f2f10a839498800cfed5fc03d726acb3d0e362","tid":1911080,"uid":38109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ee8cb9601acf741c59dcefef5a41f7e24f88a10","tid":1911080,"uid":101290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"小心啲啦，睇清楚先入，有就換個入口啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"Exactly大把入口"},{"pid":"1c59a6b07f1eab21db3a79e9a3e3108436831e74","tid":1911080,"uid":308377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ee8cb9601acf741c59dcefef5a41f7e24f88a10","tid":1911080,"uid":101290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"小心啲啦，睇清楚先入，有就換個入口啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"啱呀，一定唔好大意，千年道行一朝喪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e2c9f7067bcef5d8a3a36bf3f8f69532eeb70d","tid":1911080,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12aeae0e6baf97fe5c3b6febd4be9b8b037b428b","tid":1911080,"uid":172040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class